<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Aug1926"><font color="red">10 August 1926</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): You see where I am now but we shall have to change again &hellip; <b><font face="wake">D</font></b> is here. When I arrived I walked into a pharmacy to buy ouate. The chemist said: Are you J.J.? I said: I am. He said: I&apos;m Pat Hoey from Dublin. Hoey and Joyce are the same name. I knew him 25 years ago. </div>
